I would do the filtering only once. A new util method:
```TS
  static partition<T>(list: T[], accessor: (item: T) => boolean): [T[], T[]] {
    const truthy: T[] = [];
    const falsy: T[] = [];

    for (const item of list) {
      (accessor(item) ? truthy : falsy).push(item);
    }

    return [truthy, falsy];
  }
